 ----- Votes/Likes System requirements -------

 * Users should be able to like a post
 * Should only be able to like a post once
 * Retrieving posts should also fetch the total number of Likes

_______________________________
|                             |
|        TABLE LIKES          |
|_____________________________|

//composite-keys allow "only one" combination of two rows
//We have composite-key when there are many primary-keys

* user_id (Foreign Key from users)    // Users that going to like a photo
* item_id (Foreign key from items)    // Items that he would like

Join//
* total_likes : int                  